name: Once upon a time in future

metadata.name: Once upon a time in future #1
metadata.description:
Humans have dramatically changed the world around themselves since the beginning of their existence on this planet.
They are constantly striving to improve and fulfil their ambitious aspirations. The Internet is one such revolutionary achievement which has changed the lives of many, creating the opportunity to exist in a virtual world as well as the real world.
This is the gateway that connects the Metaverse and human physical world.

Size: 6000*4000 px
